Title: An Act Changing the Name of the Tinambacan National School of Fisheries in the City of Calbayog to Rafael Lentejas Memorial School of Fisheries
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 849
An Act Changing the Name of the Tinambacan National School of Fisheries in the City of Calbayog to Rafael Lentejas Memorial School of Fisheries
Section 1. The name of the Tinambacan National School of Fisheries in the City of Calbayog is changed to Rafael Lentejas Memorial School of Fisheries.
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.1Ã¢wphi1
Approved: April 27, 1984
